name: darth darth vader vader
description:
Awash in silver and gray with a splash of red, just like all of those expeditions with the Empire. 

Darth Vader was obviously a sexual deviant, right? It seems like one of those things that the Sith as a group would be balls- or tits-deep in. 

Mind control. Force choke. Punishment driven. In other words, an absolute Daddy.
